## Deep Technical Focus: Resin Systems
**Objective:** Balance processability, thermal–mechanical performance, and scalability

- Cure chemistry and crosslink density control
- Rheology vs impregnation behavior
- Tg vs processing window trade-offs
- Sustainability and recyclability constraints
- Scale-up risk mitigation

